  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\"><img alt=\"House Qorgyle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/50px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/75px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/100px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Gulian Qorgyle</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\"><img alt=\"House Qorgyle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/50px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/75px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c5/House_Qorgyle.svg/100px-House_Qorgyle.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\">House Qorgyle</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Qorgyle\" title=\"Quentyn Qorgyle\">Quentyn Qorgyle</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Gulian Qorgyle</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\">House Qorgyle</a>, the first son and heir of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Qorgyle\" title=\"Quentyn Qorgyle\">Quentyn Qorgyle</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Sandstone\" title=\"Sandstone\">Sandstone</a>. He has a younger brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arron_Qorgyle\" title=\"Arron Qorgyle\">Arron</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gulian_Qorgyle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Qorgyle\" title=\"Quentyn Qorgyle\">Quentyn</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/